  <entry>
    <title>春分纪日</title>
    <link href="https://poker-xh.github.io/2023/03/21/%E6%98%A5%E5%88%86%E7%BA%AA%E6%97%A5/"/>
    <id>https://poker-xh.github.io/2023/03/21/%E6%98%A5%E5%88%86%E7%BA%AA%E6%97%A5/</id>
    <published>2023-03-21T04:56:50.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-06-04T05:27:58.429Z</updated>
    
    
      
      
        
        
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;青松阴，桃花扇，不见晴空面。&lt;br&gt;浅斟低唱，无才疏狂。&lt;br&gt;风吹春水皱眉眼，哪里堪看？&lt;br&gt;从来多少春分日，沈挽芸娘，柳遇飞琼。&lt;br&gt;柴扉轻敲，桃花逗春笑。&lt;br&gt;夭夭人面何处去？拂袖残香，随春往。&lt;br&gt;空立芳海，极目缈望，&lt;br&gt;野草与碑长。&lt;/p&gt;
</summary>
        
      
    
    
    
    
    <category term="随感录" scheme="https://poker-xh.github.io/tags/%E9%9A%8F%E6%84%9F%E5%BD%95/"/>
    
